{"tid":2358278,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS5 機主討論區｜第二輪派彩 (21)我沒有我沒有沒有","createTime":"2021-01-08T04:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T12:14:49.000Z","uid":22029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"71bb29a769cb2cfc1822e8b6d92844ecf4506691","tid":2358278,"uid":22029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:27:12.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">LIHKG-PS5機主討論區</span></strong></p><br />\n <br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://gmedia.playstation.com/is/image/SIEPDC/ps5-family-image-block-01-en-16sep20?$1600px--t$\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgmedia.playstation.com%2Fis%2Fimage%2FSIEPDC%2Fps5-family-image-block-01-en-16sep20%3F%241600px--t%24&h=f9b3c248&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n <br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">Welcome to PlayStation 5 Group.<br />\n歡迎加入PlayStation 5 大家庭。</span></strong><br />\n建議新加入的玩家首先細閱下文，如再有任何問題歡迎提出。<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">想查詢購買PS5主機問題，請到友Post查詢及討論。</span></span><br />\n <br />\n[center]<strong><span class=\"x-large\">常見PlayStation Q &amp; A</span></strong></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\">新機主必睇區：</span></p><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">新機避免中BUG注意<span class=\"xx-large\">強烈建議</span><br />\n<del> 1. 熄休眠模式，唔好入休眠模式</del> (Update firmware後問題有改善)<br />\n 2. 唔好用外置HDD過PS4資料到PS5，GAME請重新入碟安裝／上PSN下載，SAVE請用PS+ CLOUD，暫時不建議用外置HDD</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">支那PS5被BAN機強烈建議唔好經非官方途徑購買PS5</span></span><br />\n詳情：<br />\nSony大量封禁支那狗PSN<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2301016\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2301016</a>"},{"pid":"e8dac6ab6aa82fb6b093f629e32be3ee5c5f85c1","tid":2358278,"uid":271339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:33:37.000Z","msg":"Q1. PSN 同PS Plus有咩關係？<br />\nA1. PSN即係PlayStation&trade;Network，其實係由Sony PlayStation&trade;提供的個人帳戶，呢個帳戶在PS主機上只用作分辨使用者從而使用其儲檔及設定。而一般玩家所提及的PlayStation&reg;Plus，是由Sony PlayStation&trade;提供的個人帳戶升級服務，當中包括多人線上遊玩，每月免費遊戲，特價折上折，優先預享特權以及自動下載更新及在線資料備份等等。<br />\n詳細有關PS Plus的介紹請往下面連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/psn/#overiew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcht-hk%2Fpsn%2F%23overiew&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=da130ef9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/psn/#overiew</a><br />\n每月PS Plus所提供的免費遊戲及其他優惠可前往下面網頁下載：<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/latest-news/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcht-hk%2Flatest-news%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=d166e841\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/latest-news/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/psn/playstation-plus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcht-hk%2Fpsn%2Fplaystation-plus%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=e0074ce4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/psn/playstation-plus/</a><br />\n**(就算未有PS主機，只可一日擁有PS Plus，你都可以用上面網頁預先下載)<br />\n<br />\n另外PS5新增PlayStation Plus Collection<br />\n只要係PS5機主及擁有PS Plus資格，會額外有20隻遊戲可以免費遊玩，包括：Bloodborne，Days Gone，Detroit: Become Human，God of War，Infamous Second Son，Ratchet and Clank，The Last Guardian，The Last of Us Remastered，Until Dawn，Uncharted 4: A Thief&rsquo;s End，Batman: Arkham Knight，Battlefield 1，Call of Duty: Black Ops III &ndash; Zombies Chronicles Edition，Crash Bandicoot N. Sane Trilogy，Fallout 4，Final Fantasy XV Royal Edition，Monster Hunter: World，Mortal Kombat X，Persona 5，Resident Evil 7 biohazard<br />\n詳情：<a href=\"https://blog.zh-hant.playstation.com/2020/10/28/20201029-psplus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.zh-hant.playstation.com%2F2020%2F10%2F28%2F20201029-psplus%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=3f9b3efe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blog.zh-hant.playstation.com/2020/10/28/20201029-psplus/</a><br />\n<br />\nQ2. PS Plus會藉可否累積上去？<br />\nA2. 可以，例子：你會藉到下一年一月完，你在本年五月購買多次12個月會藉，會藉完結日期會由下一年一月增加12個月到後一年一月。<br />\n**(用信用卡續會請緊記要自行取消自動續約，並且建議所有玩家使用雙重認證。)<br />\n<br />\nQ3. 啱啱成為機主，點登記保養？<br />\nA3. 請按下方連結前往登記頁面<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.playstation.com/zh-hant-hk/support/hardware/warranty/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.playstation.com%2Fzh-hant-hk%2Fsupport%2Fhardware%2Fwarranty%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=bff375e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.playstation.com/zh-hant-hk/support/hardware/warranty/</a><br />\n<br />\nQ4. PS5保養有無得加長？<br />\nA4. 未知<br />\n<br />\nQ5. PS5用Wifi定用LAN線直插線上網？<br />\nA5. 首選LAN線，穩定好多<br />\n<br />\nQ6. 咩係藍店<br />\nA6. PlayStation Platinum Shop，所以亦稱白金/帛金店，另有Sony Store和特許經銷商出售PS4及其遊戲<br />\n可以去下面網頁查詢各店舖位置<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/support/retail-store/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcht-hk%2Fsupport%2Fretail-store%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=82759b52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/support/retail-store/</a><br />\n<br />\n另外一種藍店<br />\n[Switch / PS4 / XBox] 黃藍黑Game舖大集合 (2)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fKDtKS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fKDtKS</a><br />\n<br />\nQ7. 數位版遊戲係唔係Load得快過實體碟遊戲？<br />\nA7. 其實兩者讀取時間一樣，分別只在於遊戲認證時會連接PSN網絡作認證還是以實體碟光碟作認證。<br />\n<br />\nQ8. 咁我應該買數位版定實體碟？<br />\nA8. 好視乎個人習慣而定。<br />\n數位版好處係當需要換遊戲時唔使更換光碟就可以直接啟動另一款遊戲，以及沒有運作光碟相應較安靜，但無法隨意出售所擁有的數位版遊戲；<br />\n而實體碟則可以在無需要PSN網絡之下進行單機認證及進行單人遊戲，以及可以輕鬆出售所擁有的遊戲實體碟，但需要空間儲存遊戲光碟和更換遊戲時需連同光碟更換。<br />\n<br />\n個人建議喺兩種情況下會選擇數位版：<br />\n當該款遊戲只提供線上遊戲而完全沒有任何單機/單人模式。<br />\n當該款遊戲會不時存取來進行遊玩，如經常會被邀請遊玩的遊戲，或知道定期會出DLC的遊戲。[/quote]<br />\n<br />\nQ9. PS5有咩擴充儲存可以用?<br />\nA9. PS5預留 M.2 NVMe PCIe 4.0 x4 規格的 SSD 擴充槽，支援2230、2242、2260、2280、22110規格，高度限制8mm，官方表示測試後會公布支援名單(暫時未有) 發售初期未支援 M.2，需待稍後更新<br />\n另外亦透過 USB 3.2 Gen 2 介面連接外接式硬碟機，但不能安裝與執行 PS5 遊戲，必須要安裝在內建 SSD 或內部擴充 SSD 上。只有上一代的 PS4 遊戲可以在外接式硬碟機上安裝與執行。"},{"pid":"88b09ffddd3da3a46bb515af56de3d9a2c16c48d","tid":2358278,"uid":139270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"屌喇星 班撚樣炒閪 次次都霸撚住啲抽獎base數 <br />\n抽幾撚多次都抽唔到啦"},{"pid":"f36ffb96ce032ec29a4aa515f62ec4448844c8fe","tid":2358278,"uid":16825,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"88b09ffddd3da3a46bb515af56de3d9a2c16c48d","tid":2358278,"uid":139270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"屌喇星 班撚樣炒閪 次次都霸撚住啲抽獎base數 <br />\n抽幾撚多次都抽唔到啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"睇死你中左咪又抽<br />\n酸撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9780a453b0a7a2a8ee4fdbaa9534e3ba03a22a23","tid":2358278,"uid":139270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f36ffb96ce032ec29a4aa515f62ec4448844c8fe","tid":2358278,"uid":16825,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"88b09ffddd3da3a46bb515af56de3d9a2c16c48d","tid":2358278,"uid":139270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"屌喇星 班撚樣炒閪 次次都霸撚住啲抽獎base數 <br />\n抽幾撚多次都抽唔到啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"睇死你中左咪又抽<br />\n酸撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"咁醒你乜都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c57427d26741eb0cd6cc701a8cc28a64d507f5","tid":2358278,"uid":20833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"今日收到電話話中，不過未有email通知<br />\n有冇人相同情況？"},{"pid":"66f83272361bb9c178795b3366c8260618e1e1cd","tid":2358278